This is a Servlet for rendering a Gephi graph based on the URI of a Pajek .Net graph.

This servlet is used by the Metalex Document Server [1] for rendering citation graphs of regulations.

[1] http://doc.metalex.eu

====
How to get things going:

* Get the latest gephi-toolkit.jar from http://gephi.org
* Get a J2EE 6 installation (e.g. Glassfish or a standalone javaee.jar)

* Deploy to a J2EE servlet container (such as Tomcat)

